Module org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql
Package org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.tools.model.query

Class JPQLQueryStateObject

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.tools.model.query.AbstractStateObject
org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.tools.model.query.JPQLQueryStateObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
StateObject
public class JPQLQueryStateObject extends AbstractStateObject
This is the root of the StateObject hierarchy that represents a JPQL query. The only child of this state object is one of the three possible query statements.
Since:
2.4
Version:
2.4
